A human-readable configuration file format

Its basically a blend of ini, toml & json
Please consider using any of those over this weekend project

```
# This is a IFFY file

[owner]
name: ImLinus
mail: mail@imlinus.com

[database]
server: 192.168.1.1
ports: [2000, 3000, 4000]
connections: 5000
enabled: true
```

returns
```
{
  owner: {
    name: 'ImLinus',
    mail: 'mail@imlinus.com'
  },
  database: {
    server: '192.168.1.1',
    ports: [2000, 3000, 4000],
    connections: 5000,
    enabled: true
  }
}
```